---
title: Saucy Turkey Ragù with Olive Tapenade
description: This twist on the classic spaghetti Bolognese is a winner! Penne replaces spaghetti, while the ragù is packed with tender ground turkey and tons of flavour! Topped with a fresh olive tapenade, this dish will have everyone in your home going back for seconds!
